====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# {{lb|zh|transitive}} to [[frighten]]; to [[scare]]
#: {{zh-x|驚嚇|to frighten}}
#: {{zh-x|嚇 死 寶寶{bao} 了！|(You) '''scared''' me! [Internet slang, usually by females]}}
#: {{zh-x|我 被 這 情景 嚇 到 了。|I was '''frightened''' by the sight.}}
#: {{zh-x|她 咳嗽 的 聲音 很 大，嚇 了 我 一 跳。|Her huge cough '''startled''' me.}}
# {{lb|zh|intransitive}} to be [[afraid]]; to be [[scared]]; to be [[frightened]]
#: {{zh-x|儂 覅 嚇 得 個。|tr=sh:6non&8veq iau&7haq teq gheq|Don't be '''scared'''.|SH}}
#: {{zh-x|伊 嚇{hiahⁿ} 一下 煞 𣍐{bōe} 講話。|He/she was scared, then could not say anything.|MN}}
#: {{zh-x|害 我 嚇{hiahⁿ} 一下。|It made me get scared.|MN}}
# to [[threaten]]; to [[intimidate]]
#: {{zh-x|恫嚇{hè}|to intimidate}}
#* {{zh-x|今 子 欲 以 子 之 ^梁 ^國 而 嚇{hè} 我 邪？|Do you wish now, in your possession of the kingdom of Liang, to '''frighten''' me with a similar scream?' (transl. James Legge) |ref=Zhuangzi}}
# {{lb|zh|Zhangzhou}} {{n-g|Used to express intimidation}}
#: {{zh-x|你 是 正 的 嚇{heeh}。|You really want to do it like this?|MN}}

