====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# {{n-g|Used to express disapproval, discontent, or resentment:}} [[tut-tut]]; [[humph]]
#: {{zh-x|嚇{hè}，豈有此理！|'''Tut-tut'''! Absurd!}}
#* {{zh-x|於是 鴟 得 腐 鼠，鵷鶵{chú} 過 之，仰 而 視 之 曰：「嚇{hè}！」|ref=Zhuangzi}}
#* {{zh-x|嚇{hè}，什麼 都 瞞 不 過 我。|ref='''1921''' January, {{w|Lu Xun}}, {{lw|zh|s:故鄉|故鄉|pref=《|suf=》}}}}
# {{n-g|Used to express astonishment.}}
#: {{zh-x|嚇{hè}，這 是 怎麽 搞 的！|'''Damn'''! How has this happened?}}
#* {{zh-x|嚇{hè}，你 看，這 多麽 好 打算？|ref='''1924''', {{w|Lu Xun}}, {{lw|zh|s:祝福|祝福|pref=《|suf=》}}}}
#: {{zh-x|嚇{hehⁿ}，是 咧{leh} 變{pìⁿ} 啥物 鬼？|What? What trickeries are you playing?|MN}}
# {{lb|zh|Hokkien}} {{n-g|Used to express a positive response}}: [[that's right]]; [[right]]
#: {{zh-x|嚇{hehⁿ}，你 講 的 著{to̍h} 是 我。|That's right, who you're talking about is precisely me.|MN}}
# {{lb|zh|Hokkien}} {{n-g|Placed at the end of a sentence to indicate doubt}}: [[isn't it so|isn’t it so?]]
#: {{zh-x|遮{chiâ} 是 恁 兜 嚇{hehⁿ}？|This is your house, isn't it so?|MN}}

